WEBVTT

01:30.830 --> 01:34.990
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.840 --> 01:39.070
[2006]

01:46.380 --> 01:51.560
[I went to your home and learned that you'd
gone to Shengcheng to earn tuition fees.]

01:51.580 --> 01:57.610
[You must finish your college anyway.
Don't ever give up on yourself.]

01:57.630 --> 02:04.010
[Please believe the sea's vast for fish
to leap; the sky's wide for birds to fly.]

02:05.310 --> 02:07.510
Wash faster! We're waiting to use them!

02:15.800 --> 02:17.430
As I wanted to escape the past

02:17.470 --> 02:18.560
and start fresh,

02:20.030 --> 02:22.079
many people and things

02:22.710 --> 02:24.640
turned into unspeakable secrets.

02:25.050 --> 02:28.900
[Episode 26 Unspeakable Secrets]

02:30.750 --> 02:31.800
The work isn't tiring.

02:31.800 --> 02:32.360
The Boss is here.

02:32.360 --> 02:32.890
Hi, Boss.

02:33.440 --> 02:34.440
Hurry up and eat.

02:34.470 --> 02:36.190
Get back to work as soon as you're done.

02:36.190 --> 02:36.990
Do you hear me?

02:37.240 --> 02:38.840
Eat up, eat up. Stop looking.

02:41.079 --> 02:42.030
Big Brother, welcome.

02:42.030 --> 02:42.590
Have you eaten?

02:42.590 --> 02:43.520
Do you want some?

02:43.800 --> 02:44.280
I just ate.

02:44.280 --> 02:45.210
Please sit down.

02:46.680 --> 02:47.880
Everything is ready.

02:47.910 --> 02:48.710
It's all good.

02:48.800 --> 02:49.310
Carry on.

02:49.310 --> 02:49.630
Take a seat.

02:49.630 --> 02:50.280
Go on with your work.

02:50.280 --> 02:51.480
Okay, I'll get going.

02:52.560 --> 02:54.290
I want more, please. A bit more.

02:54.750 --> 02:55.400
This rice.

02:56.590 --> 02:58.680
Shengcheng, as a window

02:58.680 --> 03:00.000
for the Reform and Opening-Up,

03:00.000 --> 03:01.400
bears the important position

03:01.400 --> 03:02.930
of a pioneer in this policy.

03:03.560 --> 03:04.450
In the coming years,

03:04.450 --> 03:06.100
it will develop rapidly

03:06.280 --> 03:07.560
into a modern,

03:07.630 --> 03:09.230
international metropolis.

03:09.750 --> 03:11.950
What are you looking at? Serve the food!

03:11.960 --> 03:12.710
To stand out,

03:13.080 --> 03:14.680
we need a special highlight.

03:15.610 --> 03:17.490
The infinity pool mentioned

03:17.520 --> 03:18.870
in my design proposal

03:19.079 --> 03:19.960
will make it...

03:19.980 --> 03:20.800
Look at her.

03:21.470 --> 03:22.730
You're both named Xia.

03:23.079 --> 03:24.030
But look at you!

03:26.630 --> 03:27.190
What?

03:27.400 --> 03:28.930
You got a problem with that?

03:29.030 --> 03:30.430
If I didn't give you a job,

03:30.680 --> 03:31.470
that big family of yours

03:31.470 --> 03:33.630
would've starved to death long ago,
you know?

03:33.630 --> 03:35.090
Hurry up and keep working!

03:37.630 --> 03:39.430
These are all my ideas

03:39.450 --> 03:40.380
about my design.

03:42.750 --> 03:43.350
Gong Yang.

03:44.360 --> 03:44.870
Ms. Xia.

03:45.590 --> 03:47.360
Take this file back and review it.

03:47.360 --> 03:47.710
Okay.

03:48.079 --> 03:48.960
Goodbye, Ms. Xia.

03:48.960 --> 03:49.490
Bye-bye.

03:59.560 --> 04:00.150
Ms. Xia.

04:02.520 --> 04:03.430
Were you looking

04:03.430 --> 04:04.750
at that girl in blue?

04:06.710 --> 04:08.630
She's been hanging around
all the time lately,

04:08.630 --> 04:10.400
never coming in or looking for anyone.

04:10.400 --> 04:11.860
Should we call the police?

04:11.910 --> 04:13.170
It's fine. Ignore her.

04:16.269 --> 04:17.370
Isn't that the woman

04:17.370 --> 04:19.170
who used to sell clothes at Luna?

04:19.870 --> 04:21.000
Now she's following Xia Xiaolan

04:21.000 --> 04:22.400
to construct buildings?

04:23.560 --> 04:24.970
She'd rather help an outsider

04:24.970 --> 04:26.480
than her own cousin.

04:27.070 --> 04:28.530
She sides with outsiders.

04:30.830 --> 04:31.920
We received the mortgage loan
from the bank

04:31.920 --> 04:33.560
the other day when you were
in Jiangcheng.

04:33.560 --> 04:34.390
Manager Ge

04:34.390 --> 04:35.000
has finished handling

04:35.000 --> 04:36.190
the part regarding the foundation.

04:36.190 --> 04:38.600
Shall we schedule a meeting
with Mr. Wu Daonan?

04:38.600 --> 04:39.680
Yes. You arrange it.

04:39.680 --> 04:40.070
Got it.

04:40.070 --> 04:41.190
I'll be going then, Ms. Xia.

04:41.190 --> 04:41.600
Bye-bye.

04:41.600 --> 04:42.130
Bye-bye.

04:49.360 --> 04:50.000
Hello.

04:50.240 --> 04:51.190
Can I help you?

04:52.070 --> 04:52.950
I...

04:53.750 --> 04:54.830
I'm just looking around.

04:54.830 --> 04:56.830
I don't need any help. It's all good.

04:57.040 --> 04:58.390
I see you've been coming here
quite often recently.

04:58.390 --> 04:59.880
Are you looking for someone?

04:59.880 --> 05:00.480
No, no.

05:00.510 --> 05:01.240
I see

05:01.720 --> 05:03.180
your windows are so clean.

05:03.600 --> 05:03.950
You...

05:03.950 --> 05:05.080
Nothing. It's okay.

05:09.510 --> 05:09.950
You Li,

05:10.100 --> 05:10.920
are you going to the hospital?

05:10.920 --> 05:12.040
I'll give you a ride.

05:12.040 --> 05:12.630
I-It's okay.

05:12.630 --> 05:13.600
I can go by myself.

05:13.600 --> 05:14.120
It's fine.

05:14.120 --> 05:15.040
Let's go down together.

05:15.040 --> 05:16.040
Come on. Let's go.

05:35.040 --> 05:36.040
It's you again!

05:36.510 --> 05:38.310
I didn't bring a brick this time.

05:41.159 --> 05:42.270
When I got here,

05:42.510 --> 05:43.870
she was sneaking around outside.

05:43.870 --> 05:45.270
Who was sneaking around?

05:45.390 --> 05:48.120
I'm here to see my sister!
What's wrong with that?

05:48.510 --> 05:49.310
You haven't gained any skills,

05:49.310 --> 05:50.830
but you've definitely become
more shameless.

05:50.830 --> 05:51.510
What's up?

05:51.830 --> 05:53.490
You want more cardboard? Huh?

05:53.830 --> 05:54.560
Xia Xiaolan,

05:54.750 --> 05:55.560
you're cruel.

05:55.830 --> 05:57.070
You're capable of great deeds.

05:57.070 --> 05:58.750
You're amazing, having become a big boss!

05:58.750 --> 05:59.480
But you're my elder sister.

05:59.480 --> 06:00.870
You won't even help your own sister.

06:00.870 --> 06:01.720
No matter what,

06:01.720 --> 06:03.520
you're not a good person either.

06:06.610 --> 06:08.240
I don't care! You have to help me.

06:08.240 --> 06:09.190
I don't care, anyway.

06:09.190 --> 06:10.800
I'm sticking around here! I'm...

06:10.800 --> 06:11.560
I can't deal with this.

06:11.560 --> 06:12.480
Let's go, Zhou Cheng.

06:12.480 --> 06:13.040
Sister!

06:13.190 --> 06:14.120
You can't leave.

06:16.270 --> 06:17.000
Xia Hongxia,

06:17.240 --> 06:18.900
now you know to call me Sister?

06:19.720 --> 06:21.650
If you want something, ask nicely.

06:22.040 --> 06:23.560
Call me Sister sincerely,

06:23.800 --> 06:25.000
and I'll consider it.

06:28.390 --> 06:28.870
Sister.

06:32.240 --> 06:33.100
My dear sister.

06:35.750 --> 06:37.480
I want you to help me find a job.

06:39.630 --> 06:40.750
Aren't you working

06:40.750 --> 06:41.610
for Ke Yixiong?

06:42.260 --> 06:43.680
That's not even a real job.

06:43.680 --> 06:45.430
That work is inhuman!

06:46.630 --> 06:48.159
I know you look down on me.

06:48.720 --> 06:50.560
The whole family looks down on me.

06:50.560 --> 06:52.830
I have no skills, no brains.

06:53.000 --> 06:54.920
I can't bring honor
to the family for Grandma.

06:54.920 --> 06:56.240
But I'm not loafing around,

06:56.240 --> 06:57.480
mooching off the family.

06:57.480 --> 06:58.000
Why can't I

06:58.000 --> 06:59.360
live a good life?

07:00.830 --> 07:02.690
I'm fed up with their dirty looks.

07:02.830 --> 07:05.030
I want to make a living with my own hands.

07:05.430 --> 07:06.560
I want to be like you.

07:08.660 --> 07:10.200
I want to be like you.

07:17.920 --> 07:18.450
Alright.

07:18.720 --> 07:19.450
Stop crying.

07:24.240 --> 07:26.360
Which one do you think
I should let her work on?

07:26.360 --> 07:28.560
Happy Life Materials, Luna, or Qi Hang?

07:28.720 --> 07:29.510
Are you sure you'll

07:29.510 --> 07:30.040
put her

07:30.040 --> 07:31.430
somewhere related to you?

07:31.430 --> 07:32.890
You trust her that easily?

07:33.390 --> 07:35.120
If she genuinely wants to change,

07:35.120 --> 07:36.980
she should start from the bottom.

07:37.120 --> 07:38.360
Doesn't she have

07:38.510 --> 07:40.570
the experience working in an eatery?

07:40.830 --> 07:41.560
I think

07:41.600 --> 07:42.159
we might as well

07:42.159 --> 07:43.240
let her return to her old trade,

07:43.240 --> 07:44.440
selling box lunches.

07:44.560 --> 07:45.630
It's also a way to see

07:45.630 --> 07:46.240
if she has really

07:46.240 --> 07:47.370
figured things out.

07:48.390 --> 07:49.830
You're really considerate.

07:49.830 --> 07:51.920
It's indeed not bad
to have her sell box lunches.

07:51.920 --> 07:53.380
At least she won't starve.

07:53.720 --> 07:55.040
But where should she sell them?

07:55.040 --> 07:56.430
A place that guarantees decent business

07:56.430 --> 07:57.310
and high foot traffic.

07:57.310 --> 07:59.710
And customers can't be too picky
with food.

08:01.430 --> 08:02.510
Isn't there

08:03.430 --> 08:04.890
already a place like that?

08:06.070 --> 08:06.470
Right.

08:06.680 --> 08:08.360
And we have acquaintances there.

08:08.360 --> 08:09.070
You're so smart.

08:09.070 --> 08:09.670
Of course.

08:10.310 --> 08:11.040
I'm home.

08:12.830 --> 08:13.600
I'm off then.

08:16.230 --> 08:16.760
Bye-bye.

08:17.070 --> 08:17.600
Bye-bye.

08:27.830 --> 08:29.090
Here we are. This is it.

08:30.720 --> 08:31.750
Yang and his family are

08:31.750 --> 08:32.960
going back to their hometown.

08:32.960 --> 08:34.750
So this stall is being transferred out.

08:34.750 --> 08:35.840
Don't look down on this small stall.

08:35.840 --> 08:37.900
The business is actually quite good.

08:38.030 --> 08:39.390
Well... When I worked
at Ke Yixiong's place,

08:39.390 --> 08:40.419
I was also a cook.

08:40.440 --> 08:42.000
The job you found for me is

08:42.000 --> 08:43.270
still the same.

08:44.910 --> 08:45.370
Well...

08:46.870 --> 08:47.720
Xia Hongxia,

08:47.960 --> 08:48.390
right?

08:49.750 --> 08:50.810
Take it or leave it.

08:50.840 --> 08:53.390
If you don't like it,
just go back to Ke Yixiong's place.

08:53.390 --> 08:54.920
What kind of job do you want?

08:55.390 --> 08:56.520
Do you know English?

08:56.910 --> 08:58.370
Can you deal with clients?

08:58.440 --> 08:59.700
Can you sort out files?

09:00.080 --> 09:01.750
Alright, stop provoking her.

09:02.600 --> 09:03.270
Don't be

09:03.440 --> 09:04.480
ungrateful.

09:05.200 --> 09:06.960
That pittance Ke Yixiong paid you

09:06.960 --> 09:08.760
wouldn't even cover your rent, right?

09:08.760 --> 09:09.670
Xiaolan has already rented

09:09.670 --> 09:11.390
this stall for you.

09:11.700 --> 09:13.080
From now on, you're the boss,

09:13.080 --> 09:14.810
responsible for your own profits
and losses.

09:14.810 --> 09:15.720
You don't know how much better this is

09:15.720 --> 09:17.180
than what we had back then.

09:18.510 --> 09:19.240
Xia Hongxia,

09:19.870 --> 09:20.910
I see that you're still salvageable,

09:20.910 --> 09:22.370
so I want to lend you a hand.

09:22.510 --> 09:24.270
Back then, Sis Bai sold fruit.

09:24.640 --> 09:26.910
And I also started
by selling duck eggs and oil cakes,

09:26.910 --> 09:28.710
doing these dirty, tiring jobs.

09:28.790 --> 09:30.270
Our starting points are the same.

09:30.270 --> 09:31.360
But how far you can go

09:31.360 --> 09:32.560
depends on yourself.

09:33.390 --> 09:34.670
Selling box lunches as a livelihood

09:34.670 --> 09:36.240
may not look glamorous,

09:36.480 --> 09:37.910
but as long as you aren't greedy,

09:37.910 --> 09:38.640
aren't lazy,

09:38.720 --> 09:40.510
and don't want to be a parasite anymore,

09:40.510 --> 09:41.310
then at the very least,

09:41.310 --> 09:43.110
it guarantees you won't starve.

09:46.480 --> 09:47.750
Although I don't understand

09:47.750 --> 09:49.320
the big principles you're talking about,

09:49.320 --> 09:50.960
since even Xia Ziyu couldn't beat you,

09:50.960 --> 09:52.760
you must be the more capable one.

09:53.030 --> 09:53.870
So I'll listen to you.

09:53.870 --> 09:54.930
You can't be wrong.

09:56.270 --> 09:56.730
Sister,

09:56.980 --> 09:57.870
do you want to know something

09:57.870 --> 09:58.730
about my Uncle Dajun?

09:58.730 --> 09:59.860
I'm not interested.

10:00.790 --> 10:01.890
That stall is yours now.

10:01.890 --> 10:02.730
Go tidy it up.

10:25.080 --> 10:25.740
Stop there!

10:28.550 --> 10:29.360
Tell me

10:30.000 --> 10:31.080
why you quit

10:31.080 --> 10:32.480
the job at Mr. Ke's place?

10:33.150 --> 10:35.610
Who will support you
if you don't earn money?

10:36.720 --> 10:39.120
Your Uncle Dajun, that bastard,

10:39.150 --> 10:40.440
has been lured away

10:40.440 --> 10:41.510
by that little vixen again

10:41.510 --> 10:43.480
and doesn't bring money home anymore.

10:43.480 --> 10:43.960
Grandma!

10:43.960 --> 10:45.670
How am I supposed to live?

10:45.790 --> 10:47.220
I didn't want to work there long ago!

10:47.220 --> 10:47.910
Mr. Ke

10:47.930 --> 10:49.480
didn't treat me like a human at all.

10:49.480 --> 10:50.790
I can find a job myself.

10:52.630 --> 10:53.270
I'll teach you a lesson!

10:53.270 --> 10:54.510
You hit me again!

10:54.870 --> 10:56.000
You can't control anyone now,

10:56.000 --> 10:57.660
so you just keep hitting me, right?

10:57.660 --> 10:59.260
I know you all look down on me.

10:59.390 --> 11:00.720
I have to rely on myself!

11:02.840 --> 11:03.320
You...

11:06.480 --> 11:08.110
How dare you!

11:08.110 --> 11:09.360
You little wretch!

11:09.670 --> 11:10.960
Stop crying.

11:11.550 --> 11:12.550
You're so noisy.

11:13.120 --> 11:13.840
If you scare

11:13.870 --> 11:15.000
the baby in my belly,

11:15.120 --> 11:17.120
see if Dajun will still support you.

11:17.630 --> 11:19.240
Or do you want to move out

11:19.360 --> 11:21.290
with my brother-in-law's family?

11:24.440 --> 11:27.670
You little... v-vixen.

11:27.690 --> 11:28.600
If I'm a vixen,

11:28.960 --> 11:30.290
what does that make you?

11:30.750 --> 11:31.720
And what about your grandson

11:31.720 --> 11:33.120
in my belly?

11:33.600 --> 11:35.530
Think carefully before you speak.

11:36.240 --> 11:36.670
Fine.

11:37.750 --> 11:38.240
Fine.

11:39.480 --> 11:40.280
Just you wait.

11:40.840 --> 11:42.240
Wait until my Dajun gets back.

11:42.240 --> 11:43.840
I'll have him deal with you

11:44.270 --> 11:46.330
-Seriously?
-and teach you a lesson!

11:46.440 --> 11:47.550
Our family's life is

11:47.550 --> 11:48.410
getting worse,

11:48.630 --> 11:50.440
and it's at least half your fault.

11:50.440 --> 11:52.270
You used to bully Liu Fen

11:52.440 --> 11:54.000
and Xia Xiaolan all the time.

11:54.000 --> 11:54.930
But they ended up

11:54.960 --> 11:55.870
making it big.

11:56.440 --> 11:57.870
Now you want to bully me.

11:59.200 --> 12:00.930
Dajun fell for your trick once.

12:01.150 --> 12:01.750
You think he'll still

12:01.750 --> 12:03.080
listen to you this time?

12:05.150 --> 12:05.630
I...

12:06.600 --> 12:07.030
I...

12:07.840 --> 12:09.390
This is outrageous!

12:11.330 --> 12:13.170
[Majestic Mahjong]

12:13.910 --> 12:16.440
Why can't I get a match?

12:17.240 --> 12:18.840
This is this month's income.

12:19.440 --> 12:20.640
Just this little bit?

12:25.000 --> 12:27.330
Keep playing. It's none of your business.

12:28.000 --> 12:28.600
Boss.

12:29.600 --> 12:31.720
Recently, several construction sites

12:31.720 --> 12:34.150
switched to working with the Bai's fleet.

12:35.550 --> 12:36.630
Bai Zhenzhu led her team

12:36.630 --> 12:38.630
to negotiate with them personally.

12:38.630 --> 12:40.270
The drivers are all fellow disciples

12:40.270 --> 12:41.440
from the Bai Martial Arts School.

12:41.440 --> 12:43.150
They have real kung fu skills.

12:44.840 --> 12:46.140
Besides, with Golden Sands Pool

12:46.140 --> 12:47.670
endorsing their business,

12:47.790 --> 12:49.590
for those who are not close to us,

12:49.750 --> 12:50.750
Bai Zhenzhu could easily

12:50.750 --> 12:51.750
snatch them away.

12:53.240 --> 12:55.970
Business over the past 2 months
has obviously...

12:58.030 --> 12:59.270
But this mahjong parlor is actually

12:59.270 --> 13:00.870
doing pretty good business.

13:02.750 --> 13:03.870
Mahjong parlor?

13:06.750 --> 13:08.880
I work my fingers to the bone every day,

13:09.150 --> 13:11.080
yet I'm still stuck in this mahjong parlor

13:11.080 --> 13:12.120
and make little money that's

13:12.120 --> 13:13.920
not even enough to feed you guys!

13:14.240 --> 13:14.840
Continue.

13:18.000 --> 13:20.360
Xia Xiaolan, Bai Zhenzhu.

13:21.550 --> 13:23.000
I didn't want to make enemies

13:23.000 --> 13:24.630
of two women like you,

13:25.630 --> 13:27.320
but you forced my hand.

13:30.510 --> 13:31.390
It was really not easy

13:31.390 --> 13:32.720
to invite you, Ms. Xia, to a meal.

13:32.720 --> 13:34.750
You were either in Gangdao or Jiangcheng.

13:34.750 --> 13:37.280
You weren't avoiding me on purpose,
were you?

13:37.940 --> 13:39.390
I haven't committed any crimes.

13:39.390 --> 13:41.650
Why would I avoid you, Prosecutor Jiang?

13:43.630 --> 13:44.550
I'm very sorry

13:44.960 --> 13:46.490
about what my mom did to you.

13:48.080 --> 13:49.790
You don't need to apologize to me.

13:49.790 --> 13:50.390
I actually think

13:50.390 --> 13:51.670
your mom's got a point.

13:52.080 --> 13:53.000
During the fire,

13:53.000 --> 13:53.510
your first reaction was

13:53.510 --> 13:54.870
to push Zhou Cheng away.

13:55.080 --> 13:56.510
I should thank you.

13:58.910 --> 13:59.440
No matter who was

13:59.440 --> 14:01.100
in the car with me at that time,

14:01.600 --> 14:02.030
even if it were

14:02.030 --> 14:03.690
you, whom I'm not that fond of,

14:03.790 --> 14:04.910
I would've pushed you away.

14:04.910 --> 14:05.910
It's my instinct.

14:06.600 --> 14:07.840
Of course, I also believe

14:07.840 --> 14:08.790
that if you were in my shoes,

14:08.790 --> 14:11.050
you wouldn't have left me behind either.

14:11.240 --> 14:12.670
Thank you for your honesty.

14:12.670 --> 14:15.000
And thank you
for thinking so highly of me.

14:19.720 --> 14:20.870
Zhou Cheng and I

14:21.240 --> 14:22.240
grew up together.

14:23.320 --> 14:25.780
It's fair to call us
childhood sweethearts.

14:26.440 --> 14:27.630
I do like Zhou Cheng.

14:28.120 --> 14:29.630
There's no point in hiding it.

14:29.630 --> 14:31.090
I couldn't hide it anyway.

14:31.550 --> 14:33.440
Just like the scars on my body.

14:36.120 --> 14:36.870
Besides, as long as you are

14:36.870 --> 14:37.750
not married,

14:38.120 --> 14:39.320
I still have a chance,

14:39.630 --> 14:40.120
don't I?

14:43.670 --> 14:44.840
I'm being this frank

14:45.150 --> 14:46.270
because I don't want things

14:46.270 --> 14:47.670
to be awkward between us.

14:47.910 --> 14:48.720
Nor do I want it

14:48.840 --> 14:49.910
to affect our work.

14:51.150 --> 14:52.270
Regarding the smuggling

14:52.270 --> 14:53.440
and these accidents,

14:53.440 --> 14:55.440
I also want to get to the bottom of it.

14:57.270 --> 14:58.550
I actually don't really like

14:58.550 --> 14:59.810
having a rival in love.

15:00.320 --> 15:01.980
But I appreciate your candor.

15:11.200 --> 15:12.080
If...

15:13.250 --> 15:14.360
Just if...

15:15.840 --> 15:16.600
If I hadn't

15:16.600 --> 15:17.720
come to this world,

15:19.240 --> 15:21.200
perhaps the story
between her and Zhou Cheng

15:21.200 --> 15:23.200
would have turned out differently.

15:39.720 --> 15:41.120
Mr. Wu, this way, please.

15:45.000 --> 15:45.790
Mr. Wu,

15:45.910 --> 15:47.510
do you have any suggestions?

15:47.550 --> 15:49.350
You've chosen a great location.

15:49.910 --> 15:51.640
With a pool right in the center.

15:51.790 --> 15:53.630
As long as the architecture
and environment are well-designed,

15:53.630 --> 15:54.630
it can't go wrong.

15:55.450 --> 15:57.270
Of course they're well-designed.

15:57.270 --> 15:58.320
After all, I graduated

15:58.320 --> 16:00.120
from Huaqing's Architecture School.

16:00.120 --> 16:02.320
And we have Mr. Mao
overseeing the project.

16:02.320 --> 16:02.960
Ms. Xia,

16:04.080 --> 16:06.630
could we use my consultation fee

16:06.870 --> 16:07.600
as a discount

16:07.720 --> 16:09.480
on an apartment in the Golden Sands Pool?

16:09.480 --> 16:10.550
That would be wonderful.

16:10.550 --> 16:12.080
Having you move in, Mr. Wu, would be

16:12.080 --> 16:12.810
the best advertisement

16:12.810 --> 16:14.270
for the Golden Sands Pool.

16:15.720 --> 16:17.630
This place has pleasant scenery

16:17.720 --> 16:19.870
as well as high-end facilities nearby.

16:19.870 --> 16:21.720
It's not as bustling as Gangdao.

16:22.080 --> 16:24.750
It really is a great place to live.

16:25.120 --> 16:26.750
However, I have

16:27.200 --> 16:28.530
a personal suggestion.

16:30.910 --> 16:32.970
Replace this pile of rebar with sand.

16:33.360 --> 16:34.560
Stacking it like this

16:34.710 --> 16:36.350
during construction

16:36.540 --> 16:38.140
can easily cause accidents.

16:41.790 --> 16:42.850
How's this outfit?

16:43.120 --> 16:43.850
Looks great.

16:44.200 --> 16:44.870
Will I be cold?

16:44.870 --> 16:46.730
Should I change into another one?

16:47.600 --> 16:48.150
Xiaolan,

16:48.270 --> 16:49.510
we're almost late.

16:50.320 --> 16:50.980
Okay, fine.

16:51.210 --> 16:51.740
Let's go.

16:51.960 --> 16:52.840
Okay, let's go.

16:58.670 --> 16:59.130
Hold on.

16:59.200 --> 17:00.510
I forgot the present for Zhenzhu.

17:00.510 --> 17:01.240
Xiaolan,

17:01.550 --> 17:02.610
come here for a sec.

17:03.030 --> 17:03.480
Okay.

17:03.670 --> 17:04.329
Can you go get it?

17:04.329 --> 17:05.750
It's in that bag on the table.

17:05.750 --> 17:06.109
Sure.

17:12.800 --> 17:14.210
Come on, Wei!

17:14.240 --> 17:14.880
Go for it, Wei!

17:14.880 --> 17:15.940
Do you need my help?

17:16.069 --> 17:17.880
You can't even beat one of his hands
with two of yours.

17:17.880 --> 17:18.400
Let me help you.

17:18.400 --> 17:18.750
Okay?

17:18.750 --> 17:20.440
Don't talk. I'm trying my best here.

17:20.440 --> 17:21.030
Sis Bai.

17:21.210 --> 17:21.680
Zhenzhu.

17:21.680 --> 17:22.089
Welcome.

17:22.089 --> 17:23.020
Happy Birthday.

17:23.349 --> 17:24.440
Wei, the audacity!

17:24.690 --> 17:25.680
You can't even beat Sis Bai
at arm wrestling,

17:25.680 --> 17:26.680
and you're trying to take on San?

17:26.680 --> 17:28.590
There's no shame in losing to San.

17:28.590 --> 17:29.000
I...

17:30.030 --> 17:31.830
I bought you a birthday cake.

17:32.920 --> 17:33.720
I told you,

17:33.750 --> 17:35.210
I don't do that fancy Western stuff.

17:35.210 --> 17:36.250
I ordered longevity noodles.

17:36.250 --> 17:37.200
They'll be served soon.

17:37.200 --> 17:38.480
No way, it's a birthday.

17:38.480 --> 17:39.680
You must have a cake.

17:43.160 --> 17:43.880
You know what, Sis Bai?

17:43.880 --> 17:45.080
This is the trend now.

17:45.240 --> 17:46.400
Just go with the flow.

17:46.400 --> 17:47.750
Come on, blow out the candles.

17:47.750 --> 17:48.210
Sis Bai,

17:48.400 --> 17:50.070
this is a birthday present for you.

17:50.070 --> 17:50.790
Thank you.

17:50.790 --> 17:51.640
I'll open it later.

17:51.640 --> 17:52.070
Okay.

17:53.590 --> 17:53.960
Good.

17:55.480 --> 17:58.590
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

17:59.000 --> 18:02.000
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

18:02.310 --> 18:05.920
♪ Happy birthday to me (you) ♪

18:08.110 --> 18:12.510
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

18:18.720 --> 18:19.480
Ms. Bai,

18:19.920 --> 18:22.450
I finished singing
the birthday song for you.

18:22.790 --> 18:23.350
So,

18:23.960 --> 18:26.220
aren't you going to cut me
a slice of cake?

18:28.070 --> 18:29.440
Mr. Ke.

18:30.680 --> 18:31.270
What?

18:32.640 --> 18:34.440
You couldn't win fair and square,

18:34.440 --> 18:36.100
so you came here to talk trash?

18:36.830 --> 18:38.830
Ms. Bai, are you saying

18:39.240 --> 18:41.440
that you won't show me, Ke, any respect?

18:41.530 --> 18:42.610
My Bai's fleet

18:42.640 --> 18:44.720
relies on our own skills to make a living.

18:44.720 --> 18:46.380
Why should I show you respect?

18:50.350 --> 18:51.000
Your men

18:51.030 --> 18:52.740
can't stop their shady business.

18:52.740 --> 18:54.800
Is it my fault that you lost your turf?

18:56.880 --> 18:57.720
Listen.

18:58.640 --> 19:00.310
Be it the business pie

19:00.880 --> 19:02.440
or today's birthday cake,

19:04.870 --> 19:06.600
I won't share any of it with you.

19:14.640 --> 19:15.240
Guys.

19:15.550 --> 19:16.070
Yes.

19:16.350 --> 19:17.310
Didn't we

19:17.480 --> 19:19.400
prepare a gift for Ms. Bai?

19:21.400 --> 19:22.660
Bring out the big gift!

19:40.830 --> 19:41.480
Stop!

19:57.440 --> 19:58.840
Do you want to keep going?

20:10.750 --> 20:12.240
You're all pretty tough.

20:14.510 --> 20:15.440
Since

20:15.760 --> 20:17.170
Ms. Bai and Ms. Xia

20:17.200 --> 20:18.460
won't show me respect,

20:19.000 --> 20:21.160
let's settle it in business.

20:30.550 --> 20:32.270
Tastes good. Nice cake.

20:33.270 --> 20:33.960
Let's go!

20:44.240 --> 20:44.970
Are you okay?

20:47.920 --> 20:49.030
Xiaolan, are you alright?

20:49.030 --> 20:49.560
I'm fine.

20:51.480 --> 20:52.550
That jerk.

20:53.400 --> 20:54.750
He ruined

20:54.750 --> 20:56.010
my nice birthday cake.

20:57.200 --> 20:58.440
It's okay, Sis Bai.

20:58.590 --> 20:59.200
Didn't you just say

20:59.200 --> 21:00.750
there's still a bowl of longevity noodles?

21:00.750 --> 21:01.590
As for the cake,

21:01.590 --> 21:03.320
I'll buy you another one, okay?

21:05.030 --> 21:06.510
But after the scene

21:06.720 --> 21:07.980
Ke Yixiong made today,

21:08.480 --> 21:09.750
you and San must be careful.

21:09.750 --> 21:10.590
from now on.

21:11.120 --> 21:12.160
Don't worry, Xiaolan.

21:12.160 --> 21:12.890
With me here,

21:12.920 --> 21:13.530
Ke Yixiong

21:13.560 --> 21:15.090
wouldn't dare do anything.

21:15.880 --> 21:16.750
Alright, alright.

21:16.750 --> 21:17.830
Let's eat up.

21:17.830 --> 21:18.560
I'm so hungry

21:18.720 --> 21:20.070
and running out of energy.

21:20.070 --> 21:21.070
Yes, let's dig in.

21:35.270 --> 21:35.800
Xiaolan.

21:38.920 --> 21:40.180
Has anything happened

21:40.830 --> 21:41.630
to you lately?

21:43.160 --> 21:44.090
What do you mean?

21:47.790 --> 21:48.840
I just noticed you

21:50.270 --> 21:51.200
zoning out a lot,

21:52.270 --> 21:54.070
looking distracted sometimes.

21:55.350 --> 21:56.480
What's on your mind?

21:59.480 --> 22:01.880
Maybe I've just been
swamped with work lately.

22:01.880 --> 22:02.480
I...

22:04.590 --> 22:05.920
I don't even know myself

22:06.110 --> 22:07.510
what I'm thinking about.

22:08.880 --> 22:09.960
Just now,

22:10.880 --> 22:12.030
I didn't even recognize

22:12.030 --> 22:13.090
who Ke Yixiong was.

22:31.510 --> 22:32.240
What is this?

23:38.160 --> 23:38.690
Xiaolan.

23:40.590 --> 23:42.120
First, I owe you an apology.

23:43.270 --> 23:45.070
I looked through this notebook.

23:45.550 --> 23:46.200
But I honestly couldn't

23:46.200 --> 23:47.600
understand the content.

23:48.240 --> 23:49.640
These strings of numbers

23:50.030 --> 23:51.350
look like dates.

23:52.350 --> 23:53.550
But if they are dates,

23:54.750 --> 23:57.040
there are still plenty of inconsistencies.

23:57.040 --> 23:58.480
Like "1983-8-15,"

23:58.510 --> 23:59.910
that's obviously a date.

24:01.040 --> 24:02.350
But as for "New Year's Day, 2026,"

24:02.350 --> 24:03.550
if that's also a date,

24:04.070 --> 24:06.000
that's more than 30 years from now.

24:07.960 --> 24:08.490
Xiaolan,

24:10.700 --> 24:12.160
are you hiding something?

24:13.510 --> 24:14.200
Something

24:14.830 --> 24:15.960
I can't understand,

24:16.680 --> 24:17.590
or something I

24:18.240 --> 24:19.350
can't accept?

24:20.480 --> 24:21.240
Like

24:22.480 --> 24:24.080
you're from another planet,

24:24.350 --> 24:25.070
or...

24:27.030 --> 24:28.360
you're from the future?

24:43.510 --> 24:44.200
Yes.

24:47.880 --> 24:49.010
I'm from the future.

25:01.920 --> 25:03.480
I know it's hard to believe.

25:05.480 --> 25:06.200
Honestly,

25:07.480 --> 25:09.010
I barely believe it myself.

25:13.920 --> 25:14.880
I

25:15.790 --> 25:17.200
don't really remember

25:17.960 --> 25:19.560
how it all happened anymore.

25:20.040 --> 25:20.680
I don't know

25:20.680 --> 25:21.940
how to explain it to you

25:24.350 --> 25:25.610
to make you believe me.

25:32.790 --> 25:33.400
Xiaolan.

25:36.590 --> 25:37.390
I believe you.

25:40.310 --> 25:41.030
Why?

25:42.400 --> 25:43.480
Actually, I could

25:44.830 --> 25:46.160
often feel that you were

25:46.960 --> 25:48.020
hiding something.

25:52.110 --> 25:52.790
Xiaolan,

25:54.240 --> 25:56.270
you've always had

25:57.400 --> 25:59.460
this unique courage and confidence.

26:00.740 --> 26:01.640
Sometimes you're unconventional,

26:01.640 --> 26:03.750
sometimes you're mysterious.

26:04.480 --> 26:05.790
It's all very unusual.

26:06.930 --> 26:09.210
So I've always had this feeling

26:09.240 --> 26:10.530
that you might be different

26:10.530 --> 26:11.660
from everyone else.

26:12.270 --> 26:13.930
But I couldn't figure out why.

26:15.350 --> 26:16.480
Aren't you scared?

26:30.000 --> 26:31.730
No matter where you're from...

26:34.350 --> 26:35.810
whether it's outer space,

26:36.790 --> 26:37.850
or another planet,

26:38.590 --> 26:39.400
you are still

26:40.450 --> 26:41.480
the Xiaolan I've known

26:41.480 --> 26:42.080
for years.

26:44.680 --> 26:46.080
You are still the Xiaolan

26:46.790 --> 26:47.790
I fell for

26:49.070 --> 26:50.270
the first time we met.

26:51.790 --> 26:57.500
♪ Time is so stingy,
even memories are hard to keep ♪

26:53.350 --> 26:54.150
My love for you

26:55.310 --> 26:56.000
has nothing to do

26:56.000 --> 26:57.330
with where you're from.

26:58.740 --> 27:05.600
♪ But I still remember
our promises of love ♪

26:59.510 --> 27:01.910
I only love you,
the one right in front of me.

27:06.150 --> 27:08.300
♪ Call out to me with all your strength ♪

27:08.370 --> 27:12.640
♪ Let the whole starry sky sparkle ♪

27:13.140 --> 27:15.550
♪ Respond to me with all your heart ♪

27:15.700 --> 27:20.310
♪ Across the ends of the earth,
we won't stop ♪

27:20.650 --> 27:24.610
♪ No matter how fierce the storms,
I won't back down ♪

27:24.640 --> 27:28.690
♪ I'll run toward the harbor
where you are ♪

27:27.550 --> 27:28.240
Thank you,

27:29.350 --> 27:29.920
Zhou Cheng.

27:29.520 --> 27:33.830
♪ Together, forever ♪

27:32.590 --> 27:33.200
So,

27:34.750 --> 27:36.150
the day I first met you was

27:36.960 --> 27:38.110
the day you arrived?

27:41.960 --> 27:42.960
This is also a kind

27:44.400 --> 27:46.060
of romance that belongs to us.

27:55.650 --> 27:56.310
Have you recently

27:56.310 --> 27:57.510
run into any trouble?

27:58.720 --> 27:59.400
Why did you suddenly

27:59.400 --> 28:00.400
write it all down?

28:04.920 --> 28:06.250
It's a bit complicated.

28:06.680 --> 28:07.200
I don't know

28:07.200 --> 28:08.550
how to explain it to you.

28:10.920 --> 28:11.750
Anyway,

28:12.440 --> 28:14.400
it started when I met Chen Xiliang.

28:16.120 --> 28:16.720
He is someone

28:16.720 --> 28:18.720
I'll cross paths with in the future.

28:19.590 --> 28:21.160
And ever since I met him,

28:22.400 --> 28:24.600
I seem to have forgotten a lot of things.

28:25.550 --> 28:26.480
The future me,

28:28.750 --> 28:29.680
the original me,

28:31.110 --> 28:32.110
and the current me

28:34.440 --> 28:36.300
all seem to be slowly fading away.

28:45.590 --> 28:46.160
Mr. Kang.

28:48.790 --> 28:49.400
Mom,

28:50.550 --> 28:52.610
the doctor told me to talk to you more.

28:53.160 --> 28:54.420
He said you can hear me.

28:55.750 --> 28:57.750
I've been doing pretty well lately.

28:58.640 --> 28:59.880
Ms. Xia is

28:59.880 --> 29:01.340
the best boss in the world.

29:02.440 --> 29:03.400
She trusts me

29:04.070 --> 29:05.800
and teaches me how to do things.

29:06.550 --> 29:08.080
I will definitely work hard

29:08.110 --> 29:09.270
and not let her down.

29:10.830 --> 29:11.480
Mom,

29:13.550 --> 29:14.880
if only you could wake up

29:15.960 --> 29:17.510
and see how well

29:19.110 --> 29:20.240
I'm doing right now.

29:43.480 --> 29:44.160
I see.

29:45.400 --> 29:47.800
With your memories being slowly messed up,

29:48.110 --> 29:50.110
you felt that you'd be leaving soon.

29:50.960 --> 29:51.590
So,

29:52.510 --> 29:54.830
you wanted to hurry
and fulfill your wishes.

29:54.830 --> 29:55.750
That's why you were

29:55.750 --> 29:56.950
rushing everything.

29:59.510 --> 30:00.200
And you even

30:01.110 --> 30:03.570
thought about pushing me
towards Jiang Yan.

30:05.720 --> 30:07.050
That day at the law firm,

30:07.790 --> 30:09.850
you saw me in a meeting with Jiang Yan.

30:10.930 --> 30:11.680
You didn't come in.

30:11.680 --> 30:14.510
Was it really because you didn't want
to disturb my work?

30:14.510 --> 30:15.030
Or was it that,

30:15.030 --> 30:16.360
even for a split second,

30:17.480 --> 30:19.340
you wanted to push me towards her?

30:21.510 --> 30:23.170
It was just for a split second.

30:24.350 --> 30:26.550
I didn't expect you to even notice that.

30:26.680 --> 30:28.480
But I regretted it immediately.

30:28.680 --> 30:29.310
How could I

30:29.310 --> 30:30.510
really push you away?

30:32.070 --> 30:33.400
I was just

30:34.200 --> 30:35.130
a little scared.

30:36.440 --> 30:38.640
I was afraid
that I might suddenly disappear,

30:38.640 --> 30:39.270
just like how I

30:39.270 --> 30:40.670
appeared out of nowhere.

30:41.720 --> 30:42.480
I was a bit

30:43.510 --> 30:44.310
at a loss.

30:53.750 --> 30:54.550
Then,

30:55.000 --> 30:57.330
when you first came
to this time and space,

30:57.680 --> 30:58.610
how did you feel?

31:01.400 --> 31:02.200
At first,

31:02.920 --> 31:04.960
I thought, "What the hell is this place?"

31:04.960 --> 31:06.680
Then I saw my mom, Liu Fen.

31:07.310 --> 31:10.400
I thought this Xia Xiaolan's life was

31:11.030 --> 31:12.240
really terrible.

31:13.160 --> 31:15.750
Maybe just because her life

31:16.000 --> 31:17.310
hit rock bottom,

31:17.920 --> 31:19.980
and since it was someone else's life,

31:20.310 --> 31:21.440
I had

31:21.880 --> 31:23.480
this inexplicable courage.

31:25.240 --> 31:26.070
Later,

31:27.270 --> 31:28.160
I thought

31:29.200 --> 31:29.960
if

31:30.200 --> 31:32.000
this really was God giving me

31:32.030 --> 31:33.400
a chance to start over,

31:34.440 --> 31:35.880
then I must live

31:35.900 --> 31:36.760
to the fullest.

31:42.720 --> 31:44.550
Don't look down
on the youth for being poor,

31:44.550 --> 31:46.880
and don't look down on the youth
whose ambitions are yet unfulfilled!

31:46.880 --> 31:50.540
Don't look down on the youth
whose ambitions are yet unfulfilled!

31:52.720 --> 31:54.050
Then why did you change?

31:55.110 --> 31:56.070
Why did you give yourself

31:56.070 --> 31:57.200
such a heavy burden?

32:00.030 --> 32:02.070
Yeah, why?

32:03.560 --> 32:04.590
Because I received

32:04.590 --> 32:05.790
so much love.

32:08.680 --> 32:09.350
From you,

32:10.240 --> 32:11.100
and from my mom.

32:13.310 --> 32:15.570
Because I was afraid I couldn't repay it.

32:15.790 --> 32:16.720
I was also afraid

32:17.030 --> 32:18.310
that my appearance

32:18.750 --> 32:20.150
would disturb this world

32:20.590 --> 32:23.110
and bring disaster to those around me.

32:25.070 --> 32:25.960
Like

32:26.680 --> 32:27.400
Jiang Yan,

32:27.680 --> 32:28.310
Kang Wei,

32:31.110 --> 32:31.770
and Shi Kai.

32:34.720 --> 32:35.850
Love is not a burden.

32:37.030 --> 32:37.890
Your existence

32:39.070 --> 32:40.400
will never be a burden

32:41.440 --> 32:42.680
to those who love you.

32:43.920 --> 32:45.120
It's a gift, instead.

32:46.680 --> 32:47.960
And about bringing disaster,

32:47.960 --> 32:49.420
I really have to scold you.

32:50.200 --> 32:51.330
If you weren't here,

32:51.580 --> 32:52.160
would the world

32:52.160 --> 32:53.240
be smooth sailing?

32:54.000 --> 32:55.790
Would everyone not face any misfortune?

32:55.790 --> 32:56.720
Would Ke Yixiong

32:57.160 --> 32:58.420
stop being a hooligan?

32:58.920 --> 33:00.160
And would the Du family

33:00.160 --> 33:01.360
not smuggle anymore?

33:05.590 --> 33:06.270
Xiaolan,

33:07.680 --> 33:08.610
don't be afraid.

33:09.310 --> 33:10.240
And don't worry.

33:11.680 --> 33:13.210
No matter the time or space,

33:14.030 --> 33:15.290
you can always believe

33:16.030 --> 33:18.030
that the sea's vast for fish to leap,

33:18.720 --> 33:20.650
and the sky's wide for birds to fly.

33:22.000 --> 33:23.930
Even if your memory will fade away,

33:24.580 --> 33:25.550
mine won't.

33:26.880 --> 33:28.880
I will never forget every single day

33:29.920 --> 33:30.920
I spent with you.

33:32.110 --> 33:33.160
Even if one day,

33:34.510 --> 33:35.720
you really do forget,

33:37.190 --> 33:38.720
I will tell you everything,

33:39.310 --> 33:40.750
story by story,

33:41.720 --> 33:43.050
until you get sick of it.

33:44.590 --> 33:45.070
Okay?

33:47.110 --> 33:49.440
But if I'm going to disappear eventually,

33:50.200 --> 33:51.530
wouldn't you have given

33:52.000 --> 33:53.400
all the love for nothing?

33:54.220 --> 33:55.160
And the achievements I've

33:55.160 --> 33:56.440
gained through great efforts

33:56.440 --> 33:57.510
will become just a dream ultimately.

33:57.510 --> 33:58.110
No.

34:00.350 --> 34:01.480
Even if it is a dream,

34:02.480 --> 34:03.350
as long as

34:04.270 --> 34:06.200
we give it our all without regrets,

34:07.510 --> 34:08.840
it won't be for nothing.

34:12.920 --> 34:14.520
So, do you still remember...

34:17.030 --> 34:17.960
how you got here?

34:19.300 --> 34:19.760
I don't know

34:19.760 --> 34:21.190
when I started

34:22.110 --> 34:23.639
forgetting so many things.

34:25.760 --> 34:27.159
But sometimes I feel like

34:28.590 --> 34:30.790
forgetting is actually not a bad thing.

34:31.590 --> 34:32.719
Being able to become

34:33.110 --> 34:34.840
the Xia Xiaolan I am right now is

34:34.960 --> 34:35.960
pretty good, too.

34:48.489 --> 34:49.120
Sis Bai,

34:49.150 --> 34:50.770
you've even gotten the nunchucks?

34:50.770 --> 34:51.400
Where did you get them?

34:51.400 --> 34:52.260
Check this out.

34:52.480 --> 34:54.320
A birthday gift from Xiaolan.

34:54.630 --> 34:56.280
She got this in Gangdao.

34:57.360 --> 34:58.690
Bruce Lee's signature?

34:59.030 --> 35:00.150
Personally signed.

35:00.150 --> 35:01.070
For real?

35:01.760 --> 35:02.320
Don't touch it.

35:02.320 --> 35:04.000
I'll break whichever finger touches it.

35:04.000 --> 35:05.480
It looks printed to me.

35:06.110 --> 35:07.440
Come on, let me show you.

35:14.630 --> 35:15.440
Watah!

35:17.760 --> 35:18.490
How was that?

35:19.190 --> 35:19.650
You look

35:19.810 --> 35:20.640
just like him!

35:20.670 --> 35:21.400
Cool, right?

35:21.400 --> 35:22.330
You look like...

35:23.030 --> 35:23.960
Bruce Worm.

35:24.800 --> 35:26.280
You jerk!

35:32.400 --> 35:32.920
Hello.

35:36.880 --> 35:37.880
Think it over, then.

35:37.880 --> 35:38.440
Okay.

35:38.840 --> 35:39.650
Welcome back, Xiaolan.

35:39.650 --> 35:40.280
Hi, Mr. Tang.

35:40.280 --> 35:41.080
Welcome back.

35:42.230 --> 35:44.320
If you're not going, I won't go either.

35:44.320 --> 35:45.520
Don't push yourself.

35:45.840 --> 35:46.320
Okay.

35:46.800 --> 35:47.800
I'm leaving then.

35:48.550 --> 35:49.440
I'm off. Bye-bye.

35:49.440 --> 35:49.970
Goodbye.

35:56.880 --> 35:57.810
What did Mr. Tang

35:58.360 --> 35:59.360
say to you?

36:02.970 --> 36:04.050
[Invitation
to Ms. Ji Ya's farewell banquet]

36:06.080 --> 36:06.970
Ms. Ji

36:07.000 --> 36:08.480
really embodies the word

36:08.480 --> 36:10.150
"pretentious" throughout her life.

36:10.150 --> 36:11.440
If she's going back to America, just go.

36:11.440 --> 36:12.550
Why did she send her ex-husband

36:12.550 --> 36:13.880
an invitation to her farewell banquet?

36:13.880 --> 36:15.070
Mr. Tang said

36:15.070 --> 36:16.470
he wants me to go with him.

36:16.800 --> 36:18.670
He's afraid of getting laughed at

36:18.920 --> 36:19.850
for being alone.

36:21.000 --> 36:22.800
I think neither of you should go.

36:22.960 --> 36:24.290
You can just ignore her.

36:25.630 --> 36:26.430
You should go.

36:27.070 --> 36:28.440
I mean, why not?

36:28.930 --> 36:30.110
Tang's invitation is

36:30.110 --> 36:31.880
not just about a meal.

36:32.240 --> 36:33.520
He's asking you

36:33.550 --> 36:35.190
if you're willing to officially go public

36:35.190 --> 36:36.520
with your relationship

36:36.800 --> 36:38.030
and stand by his side.

36:39.400 --> 36:41.530
Actually, I understand what he means.

36:41.670 --> 36:42.510
I'm just...

36:43.760 --> 36:45.360
I haven't made up my mind yet.

36:45.880 --> 36:46.440
Mom!

36:46.960 --> 36:48.520
Then think it over carefully.

36:48.520 --> 36:50.650
There are still a few days left, right?

36:50.800 --> 36:51.470
Granny Yu,

36:51.550 --> 36:52.320
I remember the other day,

36:52.320 --> 36:53.190
I saw some sort

36:53.190 --> 36:54.400
of Cantonese dim sum

36:54.640 --> 36:55.930
in your room.

36:55.960 --> 36:57.490
It looked quite delicious.

36:57.590 --> 36:58.400
-Which one...
-Really?

36:58.400 --> 37:00.200
Which one was it? Please show me.

37:09.670 --> 37:11.400
Why did you pull me away?

37:11.670 --> 37:12.630
Why didn't you

37:12.630 --> 37:13.960
persuade your mom to go?

37:16.150 --> 37:16.920
Granny Yu.

37:17.810 --> 37:19.080
You also know this is

37:19.110 --> 37:21.360
a big deal regarding going public
with their relationship.

37:21.360 --> 37:22.440
I think she needs to figure it out

37:22.440 --> 37:23.280
on her own.

37:23.800 --> 37:25.110
We can help,

37:25.240 --> 37:26.190
but the decision is

37:26.190 --> 37:27.480
still hers to make.

37:27.960 --> 37:29.400
Once she takes this step,

37:29.550 --> 37:31.150
her life is going to change

37:31.150 --> 37:32.470
dramatically.

37:32.760 --> 37:33.360
It is quite normal

37:33.360 --> 37:34.760
for her to hesitate a bit.

37:35.000 --> 37:36.400
So you mean...

37:37.960 --> 37:39.000
your mom will go?

37:39.510 --> 37:41.590
After all these years of training,

37:41.930 --> 37:43.680
my mom is no longer someone

37:43.710 --> 37:45.370
who doesn't know how to say no.

37:45.810 --> 37:46.960
The fact that she's hesitating

37:46.960 --> 37:48.030
shows that she still has feelings

37:48.030 --> 37:49.230
for Mr. Tang.

37:49.780 --> 37:50.580
It's just

37:50.610 --> 37:52.140
that she needs a little time

37:52.440 --> 37:53.970
to build up her confidence.

37:55.920 --> 37:56.880
So,

37:57.760 --> 37:59.280
we just do nothing?

38:01.440 --> 38:02.630
That's not it.

38:03.590 --> 38:05.250
We still need to do something.

38:29.550 --> 38:30.080
Xiaolan.

38:30.150 --> 38:31.290
Mom, perfect timing.

38:31.290 --> 38:32.110
This is the suit Chen Xiliang

38:32.110 --> 38:33.520
tailor-made specifically for you.

38:33.520 --> 38:34.200
Go try it on

38:34.230 --> 38:35.230
and see if it fits.

38:35.590 --> 38:36.300
It's tailor-made?

38:36.300 --> 38:36.830
Go ahead.

38:37.000 --> 38:38.130
This... This must be expensive.

38:38.130 --> 38:38.730
Not at all.

38:47.110 --> 38:47.670
Xiaolan.

38:48.440 --> 38:49.000
How is it?

38:49.280 --> 38:50.480
Do you think it looks good?

38:50.480 --> 38:51.360
It looks great.

38:51.840 --> 38:52.900
Look in the mirror.

38:53.630 --> 38:55.430
Isn't this color too flashy?

38:55.590 --> 38:57.190
Not at all. It suits you well.

38:57.670 --> 38:59.150
You're a totally different person now

38:59.150 --> 39:00.670
compared to before.

39:01.550 --> 39:03.180
I don't think there's any gap

39:03.230 --> 39:04.630
between you and Mr. Tang.

39:04.920 --> 39:06.250
You have your own career

39:06.360 --> 39:07.490
and your own dreams.

39:07.920 --> 39:09.980
You are also so gentle and beautiful,

39:10.000 --> 39:11.730
and you don't depend on anyone.

39:11.840 --> 39:12.840
Mr. Tang has never

39:12.840 --> 39:13.800
looked down on you.

39:13.800 --> 39:15.320
You should be more confident.

39:15.320 --> 39:17.550
Besides, look how beautiful you are now.

39:17.550 --> 39:18.360
I think

39:18.960 --> 39:20.550
Mr. Tang is the one
getting the better end of the deal,

39:20.550 --> 39:21.150
isn't he?

39:24.320 --> 39:24.920
Granny Yu.

39:25.230 --> 39:26.630
Xiaolan is right.

39:27.510 --> 39:29.770
You need to have confidence in yourself.

39:30.440 --> 39:31.710
Look at how well

39:31.710 --> 39:33.110
you're doing at your job.

39:33.230 --> 39:35.150
And you're so beautiful.

39:35.550 --> 39:37.000
Tang has good taste

39:37.190 --> 39:38.360
to have chosen you.

39:39.000 --> 39:40.710
Don't sell yourself short.

39:43.550 --> 39:44.110
Here.

39:45.400 --> 39:46.280
Put this on.

39:47.280 --> 39:47.920
Granny Yu,

39:48.320 --> 39:49.520
this is too precious.

39:50.760 --> 39:52.750
Fine feathers make fine birds.

39:53.320 --> 39:53.880
Look.

39:54.720 --> 39:56.850
Paired with the outfit

39:56.880 --> 39:58.140
Xiaolan chose for you,

39:58.150 --> 40:00.030
it's a perfect match.

40:00.880 --> 40:01.590
Granny Yu,

40:02.320 --> 40:03.110
you've brought out

40:03.110 --> 40:04.130
your hidden treasure,

40:04.130 --> 40:04.940
right?

40:06.280 --> 40:08.190
It's so beautiful. Thank you, Granny Yu.

40:08.190 --> 40:09.190
You're so biased.

40:11.000 --> 40:11.330
Look.

40:11.590 --> 40:13.790
Doesn't she look like the Mayor's wife?

40:13.840 --> 40:14.370
She does.

40:14.840 --> 40:15.360
Mom,

40:16.320 --> 40:17.780
have you made up your mind?

40:17.880 --> 40:19.010
Are you going or not?

40:21.280 --> 40:21.760
I'll go.

40:29.530 --> 40:30.280
Take it slow.

40:34.110 --> 40:34.840
Here you are.

40:36.590 --> 40:37.630
You have no idea

40:37.930 --> 40:38.850
how elegant

40:38.880 --> 40:40.840
my mom looked when she put on that suit

40:40.840 --> 40:42.110
designed by Chen Xiliang.

40:42.110 --> 40:43.360
Didn't you say before

40:43.540 --> 40:44.830
that Luna could start

40:44.850 --> 40:45.930
a high-end line

40:45.960 --> 40:47.360
to make custom clothes for others?

40:47.360 --> 40:49.320
In the future,
this will be called "Haute Couture."

40:49.320 --> 40:50.400
I think nowadays,

40:50.660 --> 40:52.590
more and more people can afford it.

40:52.590 --> 40:53.650
We can make it work.

40:54.720 --> 40:56.120
Your business mind,

40:56.150 --> 40:57.400
full of intelligence, is

40:57.400 --> 40:58.960
spinning so fast every day.

40:59.110 --> 40:59.630
Yeah.

41:00.190 --> 41:01.800
Someone told me,

41:01.920 --> 41:03.630
"The sea's vast for fish to leap

41:03.630 --> 41:05.510
and the sky's wide for birds to fly."

41:05.510 --> 41:06.510
And since then,

41:06.510 --> 41:08.000
I've only been pondering over

41:08.000 --> 41:09.670
how to make my career

41:09.670 --> 41:10.880
soar even higher.

41:11.110 --> 41:12.320
I will no longer think about those things

41:12.320 --> 41:13.380
beyond my control.

41:13.920 --> 41:14.400
Good.

41:15.230 --> 41:17.360
Then you just focus on flying.

41:17.730 --> 41:18.520
When you get tired,

41:18.520 --> 41:19.450
I'll go home

41:19.480 --> 41:21.880
and make you
noodles with fried bean sauce.

41:22.150 --> 41:22.840
Zhou Cheng,

41:23.560 --> 41:24.220
are you also

41:24.230 --> 41:25.280
a time traveler?

41:26.760 --> 41:27.820
Why do you say that?

41:28.000 --> 41:29.150
Because in the future,

41:29.150 --> 41:30.640
there will be a popular saying that goes,

41:30.640 --> 41:32.120
"Others only care

41:32.150 --> 41:33.230
how high you fly.

41:33.550 --> 41:34.230
Only I

41:34.440 --> 41:36.640
care if you are exhausted from flying."

41:37.960 --> 41:39.220
It's still different.

41:40.320 --> 41:41.670
I not only care

41:41.840 --> 41:43.320
if you are exhausted from flying,

41:43.320 --> 41:44.720
but also how high you fly.

41:45.360 --> 41:47.690
You're trying to kill me
with the rat race?

41:47.800 --> 41:48.800
What does that mean?

41:48.800 --> 41:49.550
Is this also

41:49.550 --> 41:51.350
a popular saying from your time?

41:51.670 --> 41:54.000
Then what will the world be like

41:54.400 --> 41:55.400
in the future?

41:56.360 --> 41:57.800
In the future...

41:58.550 --> 41:59.280
Come with me.

42:05.190 --> 42:07.320
In the future, this place will be filled

42:07.320 --> 42:09.710
with plenty of towering buildings.

42:10.550 --> 42:12.510
But even with all those buildings,

42:12.880 --> 42:13.840
in every city,

42:14.120 --> 42:15.070
there will still be many people

42:15.070 --> 42:16.930
who can't find a home of their own.

42:17.880 --> 42:18.320
Also,

42:18.630 --> 42:19.430
in the future,

42:20.320 --> 42:20.960
this pager

42:21.280 --> 42:22.540
will soon be obsolete.

42:22.620 --> 42:24.190
And cell phones will be eliminated, too.

42:24.190 --> 42:25.920
Everyone will have a mobile phone

42:25.920 --> 42:27.030
and can afford one.

42:27.480 --> 42:30.000
It'll be very convenient
to contact people through mobile phones,

42:30.000 --> 42:32.070
but you still won't be able to reach

42:32.430 --> 42:34.030
the people you want to reach.

42:34.880 --> 42:36.280
The speed of development in the future

42:36.280 --> 42:37.920
will be very, very fast.

42:38.510 --> 42:39.880
Everyone will be busy.

42:40.170 --> 42:41.340
And more people

42:41.360 --> 42:42.670
will leave their hometowns

42:42.670 --> 42:43.870
and head to big cities

42:43.920 --> 42:44.480
to fight

42:44.510 --> 42:45.910
for a future of their own.

42:48.630 --> 42:49.960
But that doesn't sound

42:50.760 --> 42:51.280
much different

42:51.280 --> 42:52.280
from the present.

42:54.110 --> 42:55.670
How is there no difference?

42:55.960 --> 42:58.000
By then, computers and cars

42:58.030 --> 42:59.160
will be ubiquitous.

42:59.400 --> 43:00.890
But in the end,

43:01.080 --> 43:02.150
everyone will be tied down

43:02.150 --> 43:03.880
by a tiny mobile phone.

43:07.760 --> 43:08.760
What about the others?

43:08.760 --> 43:10.160
I'm more concerned about

43:10.590 --> 43:12.250
whether we'll know each other

43:12.550 --> 43:14.030
and whether we'll be together

43:14.030 --> 43:14.760
in the future.
